# Security Policy

## Supported Versions
We provide security updates for the following versions of `@mideshn/gland-qiu`:
- Version 1.x.x

## Reporting a Vulnerability
If you find a vulnerability in `@mideshn/gland-qiu`, please report it to us at bitsgenix@gmail.com. We take security issues seriously and will respond promptly to evaluate and address the issue.

When reporting a vulnerability, please include the following information:
- Description of the vulnerability
- Steps to reproduce (if possible)
- Potential impact
- Any suggestions for a fix or mitigation

We will work with you to confirm the vulnerability and to ensure that any necessary updates are released as quickly as possible.

Thanks for helping to keep `@mideshn/gland-qiu` secure.